## Issue

Customers reported duplicate orders appearing within the application.

## Investigation

Analyzed order records and used aggregation queries to identify duplicate order IDs occurring multiple times within the orders table.

## Root Cause

Multiple records shared the same order ID, resulting in duplicate order entries.

## Resolution

Identified affected records and recommended deduplication procedures to remove duplicate entries.

## Preventive Action

Implement uniqueness constraints and validation checks during order creation to prevent duplicate records.
